snippet.title: Zanki Zero: Last Beginning Character Trailer
snippet.description:
Zanki Zero: Last Beginning comes to the PlayStation 4 and Steam in Spring 2019! The latest character trailer introduces the eight remaining survivors of humanity!

Pre-order today:

Amazon: https://www.amazon.com/Zanki-Zero-Last-Beginning-PlayStation-4/dp/B07FBFX8QW/ref=sr_1_2?ie=UTF8&qid=1531243477&sr=8-2&keywords=zanki+zero
Gamestop: https://www.gamestop.com/ps4/games/zanki-zero-last-beginning/165963
Amazon Canda: https://www.amazon.ca/Zanki-Zero-Last-Beginning-PlayStation/dp/B07FBFX8QW/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1531244765&sr=8-1&keywords=zanki+zero

Official Site: http://spike-chunsoft.com/zaz
